               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gospel of John (fols. 1v-100r)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of
                     John” (fols. 1v-100r)
 - Postscript (fols. 100r-v)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">


                     <note>The heading of the Gospel has been written on the unruled flyleaf in the
                        main hand.</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
