                        <condition key="deficient">The threads of the original binding are broken
                           and for the most part missing; the sewing has been crudely repaired by
                           recent synthetic threads. 
 The leather cover has been preserved only
                           on the inner side of the front board and on the back board. 
 The
                           first folio is made of two pieces of parchment. 
 Most of the fols.
                           are affected by humidity, held together by stitch repairs (s. fols. 1-25,
                           42-49, 95-101).
 Tears carefully amended on <locus target="#66">66</locus>, 75.</condition>
                     </supportDesc>
