               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0157DDM">Dändera Dabra Sahǝl Qǝddus Mikāʾel /
                           DDM</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1750" notAfter="1850"/>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>In the concluding supplication formula on
                        100v the space for the donor's name has been
                     left unfilled (unless the name is Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer); the name of Gabra
                     Giyorgis is written in a supplication, in a later, crude hand(100v). Currently, the Ms. is in private possession
                     of peasant ʿālam Gabra Māryām.</provenance></history>
